The evidence with the title 'Pelosi touts Democrats' revival of 'pay-as-you-go' budget rules ... ' says Feb 10, 2010  ... President Barack Obama has often praised PAYGO , though PolitiFact ruled that his april 2009 claim that paygo " helped transform large deficits into surpluses in the 1990s " was an exaggeration and Half True. More recently, House speaker Nancy Pelosi , D-Calif., made a point of praising paygo. 
